{"title":"Nerd Alert Podcast: Nerding out on custom wheels","link":"https://cyclingtips.com/2021/02/nerd-alert-podcast-nerding-out-on-custom-wheels/","date":1613042541000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><article data-block-name=\"post-aside\"><div><div><p>In this week’s Nerd Alert, James and Dave go deep into the rabbit hole of custom bicycle wheels with Adrian Emilsen of Melody Wheels in Perth, Australia.</p></div><div><p><img width=\"1340\" height=\"754\" data-src=\"https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-1340x754.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-1340x754.jpg 1340w, https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-650x366.jpg 650w, https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-190x107.jpg 190w, https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-16x9.jpg 16w, https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1340px) 100vw, 1340px\" src=\"https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-1340x754.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-1340x754.jpg 1340w, https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-650x366.jpg 650w, https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-190x107.jpg 190w, https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner-16x9.jpg 16w, https://cdn-ctstaging.pressidium.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/wheel-banner.jpg 1920w\"></p></div></div><div><div><p>Why should you care about wheels? Are custom wheels really better than factory-built ones? How would you build a set of wheels for a light rider versus a heavier one? What are some strategies you can pursue at home if you want to get into the basics of tru